{"id":232098711,"title":"【酒吧心得】台中科博館附近的\"居有酒\"(單杯葡萄酒專賣)","content":"我是一個晚上很喜歡跑來跑去也喜歡四處喝酒的人，偶然路過這間位於科學博物館附近的葡萄酒單杯店，前幾日就來這裡打發一下時間了。\n\n店裡從下午開始就有人了，目前就一個很性格的老闆駐店。\n我點了兩杯葡萄酒，一杯價格250元/100毫升\n\n第一杯是奧地利的原生葡萄 Gruner Veltliner( 綠菲特麗娜 )所釀造的白葡萄酒，走的是清爽路線。喝起來有點酸度，蠻解悶的。\n第二杯紅酒，只記得是五種葡萄混釀的，光聞起來有種熟桑葚的甜感，喝下去的味道雖然有深度，但不算是我喜歡的口感，就不多賣弄了。\n\n有機會可以去試試，他們也有臉書專頁，\nhttp://i.imgur.com/rIkMzS1.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/tg69KUw.jpg","excerpt":"我是一個晚上很喜歡跑來跑去也喜歡四處喝酒的人，偶然路過這間位於科學博物館附近的葡萄酒單杯店，前幾日就來這裡打發一下時間了。店裡從下午開始就有人了，目前就一個很性格的老闆駐店。我點了兩杯葡萄酒，一杯價格","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"23082c2f-c19d-456c-a805-1e6ac0a36c31","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-09-16T08:39:14.114Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-16T08:39:14.114Z","commentCount":1,"likeCount":27,"tags":[],"topics":["葡萄酒","酒吧","台中"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"品酒","forumAlias":"alcohol","school":"國立臺中科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":27}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/rIkMzS1.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/tg69KUw.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"df3d6a05-9fce-41b4-ba16-77a2dc28e660","url":"https://i.imgur.com/rIkMzS1l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/rIkMzS1l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/rIkMzS1l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-09-16T08:39:14.114Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-16T08:39:14.114Z"},{"id":"df3d6a05-9fce-41b4-ba16-77a2dc28e660","url":"http://i.imgur.com/rIkMzS1.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/rIkMzS1","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/rIkMzS1l.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-09-16T08:39:14.114Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-16T08:39:14.114Z"},{"id":"9f241d20-136e-4228-9d95-3468f2dd4cb6"